# RiftBot Lua & Walker Snippets

A reference of single-line `lua:` walker entries, native walker conditions/states, and helper calls for RiftBot.

> **How to read this**
> - `lua:` lines go in the walker as a single Lua statement (chain statements with spaces, **never** newlines).
> - `goto:` and `state:` lines are **native walker config**, not Lua.
> - Item IDs / monster names / channel ids are **examples** — replace with your server's.
> - Lines marked _(test)_ were inferred from spotted scripts, not confirmed from public module scripts — verify once before relying on them.

