## Supplies & Logout
```lua
lua: if Self.ItemCount(8309) < 100 then Walker.Goto("DepotRefill") end
```
Low on mana fluids → route to your refill label.
```lua
lua: if Self.ItemCount(8309) < 100 then Walker.Enabled(false) Self.Logout() end
```
Out of supplies → stop the walker and log out.
```lua
lua: local w=Self.Weapon() local n=Self.ItemCount(7368)+((w and w.id==7368) and w.count or 0) if n<400 then Walker.Enabled(false) Self.Logout() end
```
Counts assassin stars **including the equipped hand stack**, logs out under 400.

