## Buying
*(servers using "instant buy/withdraw" chat commands)*
```lua
lua: local n=math.floor((Self.Capity()-50)/1.80); if n>0 then Self.Say("instant buy "..n.." mana fluid") end
```
Buy enough manas to fill cap, leaving 50 free (1.80 oz each).
```lua
lua: Self.Say("instant withdraw "..(500*55))
```
Withdraw gold for a fixed 500 manas (55 each).
```lua
lua: local need=500-Self.ItemCount(8309); if need>0 then local f=math.floor((Self.Capity()-50)/1.80); local x=math.min(need,f); if x>0 then Self.Say("instant buy "..x.." mana fluid") end end
```
Buy up to 500, capped to what fits — never spam-buys with no cap.
```lua
lua: if Self.ItemCount(8309) < 500 then Self.Logout() end
```
After buying, if still under 500 (no cap or no money) → log out.

