## Conditional Routing
```lua
lua: if Self.HealthPercent() < 40 then Walker.Goto("RunAway") end
```
Low HP → jump to an escape label.
```lua
lua: if Self.ItemCount(8309) >= 500 then Walker.Goto("ToSpawn") end
```
Already stocked → skip buying.
```lua
lua: if Self.Capity() < 50 then Walker.Goto("DropLoot") end
```
Cap nearly full → go offload loot.

