## Position Checks
```lua
lua: local p=Self.Position() if p.x==32410 and p.y==32179 and p.z==7 then Walker.Goto("AtTile") end
```
Exact tile match.
```lua
lua: if Self.Position().z ~= 7 then Walker.Goto("WrongFloor") end
```
Wrong floor → recover.
```lua
lua: local p=Self.Position() if p.x>=32400 and p.x<=32450 and p.y>=32170 and p.y<=32200 then Walker.Goto("InSpawn") end
```
Inside an area box (e.g. "am I in the spawn?").
```lua
lua: local p=Self.Position() if not (p.z==7 and math.abs(p.x-32410)<=2 and math.abs(p.y-32179)<=2) then Walker.Goto("RetryLabel") end
```
Arrival check: if not within 2 sqm of the target tile (and right floor), go back to a label.
```lua
lua: Self.WalkTo(32410, 32179, 7)
```
Path to a tile from inside Lua. _(test)_

