## Equipment Swaps
```lua
lua: Self.EquipItem(SLOT_FEET, 3079, 1)
```
Boots of haste on.
```lua
lua: Self.EquipItem(SLOT_FEET, 8761, 1)
```
Energy boots on.
```lua
lua: Self.EquipItem(SLOT_RING, 3053, 1)
```
Time ring on.
```lua
lua: Self.DequipItem(SLOT_RING)
```
Take the ring off (empties the slot). `EquipItem` from your bag auto-swaps whatever's worn.
```lua
lua: if Self.Position().z == 14 then Self.EquipItem(SLOT_FEET,8761,1) else Self.EquipItem(SLOT_FEET,3079,1) end
```
Auto boots by floor (energy boots on the spawn floor, haste elsewhere).

