## Doors & Ground Items
```lua
lua: Self.UseItemFromGround(31928, 32633, 10)
```
Use a fixed door/lever at exact coords (works from either side).
```lua
lua: Map.UseItem(32413, 32230, 10)
```
Same idea via the `Map` namespace — interchangeable; if one fails on a door, try the other. _(test)_
```lua
lua: local p=Self.Position() Self.UseItemFromGround(p.x, p.y+1, p.z)
```
Use the tile to your **south** (relative). North = `p.y-1`, East = `p.x+1`, West = `p.x-1`.

