## Mana / Cooldown Gates
*(hold the node until a condition is met)*
```lua
lua: while Self.Mana() < 900 do wait(250,500) end
```
Don't advance until mana ≥ 900.
```lua
lua: local t=os.time() while Self.Mana() < 900 and os.time()-t < 30 do wait(250,500) end
```
Same, with a 30s safety timeout so it can't hang forever.
```lua
lua: while #Creature.iMonsters(5,false) > 0 do wait(500) end
```
Wait until no monsters within 5 sqm before moving on.

