## Crowd & Safety
```lua
lua: if #Creature.iPlayers(8,false) > 0 then Walker.Goto("Hide") end
```
Any player on screen → react.
```lua
lua: for _,p in ipairs(Creature.iPlayers(8,false)) do if string.lower(p.name)=="badguy" then Walker.Enabled(false) Self.Logout() end end
```
A specific named player appears → stop & log out.
```lua
lua: if #Creature.iMonsters(7,false) == 0 then Self.Say("exura gran") end
```
Heal only when the screen is clear of monsters.
```lua
lua: if #Creature.iMonsters(1,false) >= 3 then Self.Say("exori") end
```
3+ monsters adjacent → cast an AoE.

