## Target-Based
```lua
lua: if Self.TargetID() <= 0 then Walker.Goto("FindTarget") end
```
Nothing targeted → go find one.
```lua
lua: local c=Creature.getCreatures(Self.TargetID()) if table.count(c)>=2 and c.hpperc<=15 then Self.Say("exori vis") end
```
Finish a low-HP target with a cheap spell.
```lua
lua: Targeting.setAttackMode("follow")
```
Chase/melee the target — close in for melee or to line up `exevo mort hur`. _(test)_
```lua
lua: Targeting.setAttackMode("distance")
```
Keep distance / kite. _(test)_
```lua
lua: Targeting.setAttackMode("stand")
```
Hold position (don't move toward the target). _(test)_

