## Time-Gated Actions
*(globals persist between firings — note the missing `local`)*
```lua
lua: if not _ringT or os.time()-_ringT>180 then Self.EquipItem(SLOT_RING,3051,1) _ringT=os.time() end
```
Re-equip an expiring ring at most every 3 minutes.
```lua
lua: if not _alarmT or os.time()-_alarmT>10 then Rifbot.PlaySound("a.mp3") _alarmT=os.time() end
```
Throttle an alarm to once per 10 seconds.

