## Misc / Anti-Idle
```lua
lua: Self.Turn(math.random(0,3))
```
Random turn — small anti-idle nudge. Directions: `0=N, 1=E, 2=S, 3=W`.
```lua
lua: if not Self.isConnected() then Rifbot.PressKey(13, 2000) end
```
