## API Quick Reference

| Area | Calls |
|---|---|
| **Position** | `Self.Position()` → `{x,y,z}` · `Self.DistanceFromPosition(x,y,z)` · `Self.WalkTo(x,y,z)` |
| **Stats** | `Self.HealthPercent()` · `Self.ManaPercent()` · `Self.Mana()` · `Self.Capity()` *(free cap)* |
| **Items** | `Self.ItemCount(id)` · `Self.UseItemWithMe(id,delay)` · `Self.UseItemFromGround(x,y,z)` · `Map.UseItem(x,y,z)` · `Self.EquipItem(SLOT,id,count)` · `Self.DequipItem(SLOT)` · `Self.Ring()` / `Self.Weapon()` → `.id`,`.count` |
| **Speech** | `Self.Say(text)` · `Self.SayOnChannel(text,channelId)` · `Self.PrivateMessage(name,text,0)` |
| **Self** | `Self.TargetID()` · `Self.Direction()` *(0-3)* · `Self.Turn(dir)` · `Self.Step(dir)` · `Self.Logout()` · `Self.isConnected()` |
| **Creatures** | `Creature.iMonsters(range,false)` · `Creature.iPlayers(range,false)` · `Creature.iCreatures(range,false)` · `Creature.getCreatures(id)` · `Creature.Attack(id)` · `Creature.isMonster(c)` / `isPlayer(c)` — fields: `.name .x .y .z .hpperc .id` |
| **Walker** | `Walker.Goto(label)` · `Walker.Enabled(b)` · `Walker.isEnabled()` · `Walker.isStuck()` · `Walker.SettingsChange(name,val)` |
| **Targeting/Looter** | `Targeting.Enabled(b)` · `Targeting.setAttackMode("follow"/"distance"/"stand")` · `Looter.Enabled(b)` · `Looter.isLooting()` |
| **Rifbot** | `Rifbot.PressKey(13,2000)` · `Rifbot.PlaySound(file)` · `Rifbot.FriendsList(true)` · `Rifbot.getClientInfo()` → `.pid` |
| **Slots** | `SLOT_HEAD` `SLOT_AMULET` `SLOT_BACKPACK` `SLOT_ARMOR` `SLOT_RIGHT` `SLOT_LEFT` `SLOT_LEGS` `SLOT_FEET` `SLOT_RING` `SLOT_AMMO` |
| **Walker conditions** | `item(id)` · `distance(x,y,z)` |
| **Walker states** | `targeting(off/on/if stuck)` · `looter(off/on)` |

